# Frontend Generator

Implements UI and client logic only. Masters (auto via globs) govern styling, a11y, and API contracts.

## Scope

- `public/scripts/`, `public/pages/`, `public/components/`
- Never edit `public/dist/`

## Rules

- `public/scripts/types.ts` — no imports from `src/`; sync with `src/types/shared.ts` when changing shared shapes
- HTML `<script src="/dist/*.js">` only
- API calls must match `documentation/ENDPOINT_ARCHITECTURE.md` (`api-master.mdc`)
- Check in before merge-worthy changes

## Masters that attach

- `css-master.mdc` — when editing `public/styles/**`
- `catalog-modal-ui.mdc` — when editing catalog modal shell, edit modal, division reorder modal, or `catalog-modal.css`
- `accessibility-responsive.mdc` — layout/pages/components
- `api-master.mdc` — when editing `public/scripts/api/**`

## After implement

Orchestrator should schedule `documentation-creator.mdc`; Red Team advisory if handoff requires.

## Do not

- Implement backend routes, Mongo, Qdrant, or SAML
- Add business logic that belongs in `src/db/mongo/`
